uh, him leaving Utah now?

05:35.835 --> 05:38.296
Well, that's just kismet.
Lady luck.

05:38.379 --> 05:40.965
We play his brand of
offense, he slots right in.

05:41.049 --> 05:43.760
And if we pull
the trigger soon...

05:43.843 --> 05:45.720
Well, he's still got time
to make some changes

05:45.803 --> 05:47.388
and make the team his own.

05:47.472 --> 05:48.973
I'm telling you.
It's shit

05:49.057 --> 05:51.517
-or get off the pot.
-Alright.

05:51.601 --> 05:53.394
