05:53.478 --> 05:55.146
And what happens
when McKinney's ready?

05:55.229 --> 05:57.231
Well, that's going
to be the problem.

05:57.315 --> 05:59.567
No coach worth his salt is
going to come in as a temp,

05:59.650 --> 06:01.819
so you'll have to make Elgin...

06:01.903 --> 06:04.155
