Bill. I mean, shit.

06:10.995 --> 06:12.371
Your best bet's
in the hospital,

06:12.455 --> 06:14.749
you got Hamlet on the sideline
looking for his fuckin' dick.

06:14.832 --> 06:17.085
All I'm saying is "interim."

06:18.836 --> 06:21.714
It must end. It's what
the fuckin' word means.

06:21.798 --> 06:24.258
You have to put your chips
on someone soon,

06:24.342 --> 06:26.677
or you can kiss
the fuckin' season goodbye.

06:30.348 --> 06:31.641
Fuck a duck.

06:47.198 --> 06:48.866
Crisscross applesauce.

06:49.367 --> 06:50.243
What?

06:50.326 --> 06:52.453
