on the fast break.

49:06.276 --> 49:07.653
Team one for Chaney.

49:07.736 --> 49:09.154
I tell you, these refs
must be blind.

49:09.237 --> 49:10.822
Another good no-call
by the officials! Ha!

49:10.906 --> 49:13.492
Motherfucker!
What is you doing?

49:13.575 --> 49:15.869
-Use the goddamn whistle!
-Please, ref. Please!

49:18.538 --> 49:21.708
Fuckin' fuckin' fuck!

49:21.792 --> 49:23.877
And this is just
an abomination.

49:23.960 --> 49:25.754
Jamaal taking
a football blow.

49:25.837 --> 49:27.756
Somehow,
no whistle from the refs.

49:27.839 --> 49:29.007
Absolutely despicable.

49:29.091 --> 49:30.592
...not letting the Lakers
get away with dirty tricks.

49:34.680 --> 49:37.057
Nixon tripped
and takes a header.

49:37.140 --> 49:38.308
Not a whistle to be heard.

49:38.392 --> 49:40.018
Boy, if I didn't
know any better,

49:40.102 --> 49:41.937
I'd say these refs
were on the Boston payroll.

49:42.020 --> 49:43.438
Call it,
call the fuckin'--

49:43.522 --> 49:46.191
This is the best officiated
game in years!

49:46.274 --> 49:48.360
This cornbread
motherfucker--

49:48.443 --> 49:50.362
Cooper trips over his feet.

49:50.445 --> 49:52.531
These Lakers are looking
awfully clumsy tonight.

49:52.614 --> 49:54.324
Officials are swallowing
their whistles once again.

49:54.408 --> 49:58.036
Shut down the fuckin' act,
you motherfucker!

49:58.120 --> 50:00.706
Johnson looking desperate
under the rim.

50:00.789 --> 50:03.083
Open your fuckin' eyes!

50:03.166 --> 50:04.126
He's on his arm!

50:04.209 --> 50:06.044
And Johnson hits the deck,

50:06.128 --> 50:07.838
making a show of it
for the officials

50:07.921 --> 50:09.589
but they're not buying
what he's selling.

50:09.673 --> 50:10.966
Fuckin' call it!

50:11.049 --> 50:12.426
Goddamn it.

50:12.509 --> 50:14.678
This fiddle-faddle officiating
may cost the Lakers the game.

50:14.761 --> 50:16.805
But the refs call it
like they see it

50:16.888 --> 50:19.975
and what they see is good,
clean fun from Boston.

50:22.185 --> 50:23.437
Another--

50:23.520 --> 50:24.771
It's just a fuckin' game, Jerry.

50:24.855 --> 50:26.732
Nothing but net!

50:26.815 --> 50:29.317
Boston boy is on fire tonight!

50:29.401 --> 50:31.778
Celtics fan:
Go home, you fuckin' pussies!

50:31.862 --> 50:33.655
Third quarter,
and the Celtics...

50:33.739 --> 50:35.615
-God fuck.
-...for a commanding lead.

50:35.699 --> 50:37.951
If substitute coach
Paul Westhead

50:38.034 --> 50:40.412
wants to prove
he's not just wearing diapers,

50:40.495 --> 50:42.539
now's his chance
to put on big-boy pants

50:42.622 --> 50:44.416
and raise his hand.

50:44.499 --> 50:47.002
You gotta make a sub.
Make a sub.

50:53.425 --> 50:54.968
Wood.

50:56.553 --> 50:59.222
After an onslaught of
egregious uncalled fouls

50:59.306 --> 51:01.892
for the boys in green,
Spencer Haywood
has had enough.

51:01.975 --> 51:03.894
He's gonna
clean it up himself, folks.

51:03.977 --> 51:05.645
Johnson passes to Haywood.

51:05.729 --> 51:07.481
Haywood with
a hand-off to Nixon.

51:07.564 --> 51:09.858
Nixon, jumper. It's good!

51:11.985 --> 51:13.695
Bird hooks by Coop
with an elbow.

51:13.779 --> 51:16.823
No call. Oh!
He ran into a brick wall
in Spencer Haywood.

51:16.907 --> 51:19.576
-Boom!
-The dropped shoulder
laid Bird on his back!

51:19.659 --> 51:22.454
Bird looks like he's had
just about enough of this.

51:22.537 --> 51:24.539
...Bird chucks the ball at
Spencer, throwing a tantrum.

51:24.623 --> 51:25.999
Punches are being thrown.

51:26.082 --> 51:27.667
The Celtics
are throwing punches.

51:27.751 --> 51:30.337
We've got fisticuffs, folks.
The benches are clear.

51:30.420 --> 51:32.756
The Celtics are absolutely
out of control.

51:34.508 --> 51:36.259
The Lakers are acting
like hoodlums, hoodlums!

51:36.343 --> 51:39.346
-And here's a late
whistle from the officials.

51:39.429 --> 51:41.181
Technical foul
on Spencer Haywood.

51:41.264 --> 51:43.266
It's a technical
on Spencer Haywood.

51:43.350 --> 51:44.351
Well, I cannot
believe my eyes.

51:44.434 --> 51:46.102
No! That was 33!
Come on, ref!

51:46.186 --> 51:49.064
You gotta get in there!
Hey! Hey, Earl!

51:49.147 --> 51:51.483
You blind fuck!
Now, you see us,
do you, huh?

51:51.566 --> 51:53.985
Now--
Halle-fucking-lujah!

51:54.069 --> 51:56.530
-It's a miracle.
-Welcome back, Pat.

51:56.613 --> 51:59.157
-Enjoy your first tech.

52:09.543 --> 52:12.712
Bravo! At least
he fucking earned it!

52:12.796 --> 52:14.840
That's your first
honest call of the night!

52:14.923 --> 52:17.759
Watch it, Coach!
I'm about to throw you
out of this game.

52:17.843 --> 52:19.845
You've been
screwing us all night!

52:19.928 --> 52:22.013
-- What did you say?
-- Paul. That's enough!

52:22.097 --> 52:24.224
I said I was screwing
your wife last night!

52:24.307 --> 52:26.643
-Shit!

52:26.726 --> 52:28.228
You're outta here!

52:28.311 --> 52:30.188
It's okay. It's okay.

52:30.272 --> 52:32.816
You're up, Coach.

52:32.899 --> 52:36.027
Celtics fan: Hey, Riley!
Eat a bag of dicks, ya bitch!

52:37.779 --> 52:39.948
-Fuck Boston!

52:42.826 --> 52:44.995
Bring it in!
Calm down!

52:45.078 --> 52:46.913
Shh. Take a breath.

52:48.790 --> 52:51.126
Repeat after me. Fuck Boston.

52:51.209 --> 52:53.503
-Fuck Boston. Fuck Boston!
-Fuck Boston! Fuck Boston!

52:53.587 --> 52:56.256
-Fuck Boston! Fuck Boston!
-Fuck Boston! Fuck Boston!

52:56.339 --> 52:58.174
We're not gonna lose
this fucking game!

52:58.258 --> 53:01.094
-Get out there
and kick their ass!
-Whoo!

53:01.177 --> 53:03.597
The Lakers are fed up,
fired up,

53:03.680 --> 53:04.973
and they're fighting mad.

53:05.056 --> 53:06.600
-Yes!

53:10.020 --> 53:12.063
And a tone-shift has
happened for the Lakers here.

53:12.147 --> 53:13.648
They have reclaimed
the momentum,

53:13.732 --> 53:16.359
and Westhead
is looking commanding
on the sidelines.

53:16.443 --> 53:19.237
One blown call after another
and the officials have let

53:19.321 --> 53:21.406
the Lakers make a game of it!

53:29.331 --> 53:31.791
Alright, out of the time-out,
Lakers take the floor.

53:31.875 --> 53:33.668
Let's see what Professor
Westhead's come up with.

53:33.752 --> 53:34.961
Celtics Fan
Come on, Larry,
eat 'em up!

53:35.045 --> 53:36.630
Celtics Fan
Eat his stinkin' shit,
Lakers!

53:36.713 --> 53:38.131
Keeping it inbound,
right side.

53:38.214 --> 53:40.425
Referee hands him the ball,
looking for a place to go.

53:40.508 --> 53:43.136
He finds Magic top of the team.
Magic at the three-point line,

53:43.219 --> 53:44.971
dribbling up and down
like a yo-yo.

53:45.055 --> 53:47.349
Magic surveying the floor.
There's nowhere to go with it.

53:47.432 --> 53:48.975
The clock is winding down.
Ten seconds.

53:49.059 --> 53:51.353
Coop, set the pick!

53:51.436 --> 53:53.438
Magic makes a move,
loses Bird.

53:53.521 --> 53:55.607
No-look to Cooper. Hit hard.

53:55.690 --> 53:58.151
Throws up a prayer...

54:02.864 --> 54:04.282
Off the iron...

54:04.366 --> 54:06.993
Holy shit!

54:07.077 --> 54:09.162
-Gets a bounce
and goes in!

54:09.245 --> 54:11.122
Unbelievable!
Right at the buzzer.

54:11.206 --> 54:14.751
-Michael Cooper with
a game-winning--

54:17.295 --> 54:19.172
-Coop!
-Yes!

54:19.255 --> 54:21.716
Lakers win
a hard-fought victory

54:21.800 --> 54:24.636
here on the parquet floor
in Boston.

54:26.471 --> 54:28.515
The Lakers have
beaten biased referees,

54:28.598 --> 54:30.225
-a heated crowd...
-Fuck!

54:30.308 --> 54:31.726
They stole it from Boston!

54:31.810 --> 54:33.478
Absolutely stole it!

54:33.561 --> 54:34.980
Boy, oh, boy
is this crowd silent.

54:42.487 --> 54:43.697
Celtics fan:
Aw, fuck!

54:48.451 --> 54:52.163
Yes! Yes, yes, yes!

54:52.247 --> 54:54.833
Magic Johnson is smiling
like the sun.

54:54.916 --> 54:57.377
We may be looking at
Rookie of the Year here,
folks.

54:57.460 --> 54:59.462
-Larry!
-Leave me the fuck alone.

54:59.546 --> 55:01.297
Larry, any comment
on the game?

55:02.007 --> 55:03.925
He mad, y'all.

55:06.136 --> 55:08.263
Ha, ha. Unbelievable.

55:08.346 --> 55:10.181
Wherever Jack McKinney is
watching, I hope he's proud

55:10.265 --> 55:13.476
of his team and proud
of Paul Westhead right now.

55:15.186 --> 55:17.272
Signs of life last night
for the Lakers

55:17.355 --> 55:19.357
as they managed
to defeat the Celtics

55:19.441 --> 55:21.526
on their turf in Boston.

55:30.118 --> 55:31.202
Big win.

55:33.246 --> 55:34.330
Barely.

55:43.757 --> 55:45.759
If I wait for you,

55:45.842 --> 55:47.969
and you don't make it back...

55:51.014 --> 55:53.558
then I'm stuck with Westhead.

55:53.641 --> 55:56.519
And I'm not gonna win
a title with him, am I?

56:01.149 --> 56:02.484
No.

56:03.359 --> 56:05.153
That's what I thought.

56:23.755 --> 56:26.341
We're not done
playing yet, Jack.

56:34.849 --> 56:36.267
Fuck Boston.
